{"tid":1860261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"光復後建議增設市政警察","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T04:12:39.000Z","uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1612e0baeeb32060427683fa93fc579716dacf3","tid":1860261,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"環境保護署內設市政警察總隊保護香港資源，總隊隊長向環保署市政副署長負責，食環署環境衞生部分及漁護署漁農部分亦併入環保署<br />\n<br />\n總隊以水警為基礎擴編，負責動物保護、環境保護、水警、漁業農地保護、重建遷移執法、地政非法佔用執法、緊急醫療救護、衞生署及醫管局保安、流行病人入院令執行等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63Qm1AJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63Qm1AJ.png&h=0b9fdf1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消滅中華極權 重現諸夏榮光 最美好的未來世界地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUXDWgo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUXDWgo.png&h=b065979b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77698f3cc7c8793cf8c89b7d6a83651580bbac6a","tid":1860261,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"(劣政人禍)瘟疫下只有美金及黃金值錢換定唔怕盲搶<br />\n<br />\n(應急師)今次武肺的教訓係每個人要儲備應急物資，今次捱得過，除左要集資起口罩廠，仲要定期儲備應急密資，天助自助者，不但助己，仲可以助人，黃色應急圈互相送/賣應急物資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jGmLU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jGmLU.png&h=e55594c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a48b112752cad421f97368f25e3cc7a2bf50c63","tid":1860261,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"記者入"},{"pid":"7a12a585d93ec00689f0eaf46590570666a1afe4","tid":1860261,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0y4A7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0y4A7b.png&h=1e970816&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}